<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Blog</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>My Personal Blog</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="btn">Home</a>
            <a href="/posts/new" class="btn">New Post</a>
            <a href="#recent-posts" class="btn">All Posts</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="about-container">
            <div class="about-image">     
                <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Profile" class="profile-photo">
            </div>
            <section class="about-me">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Hey there! I'm Saloni — a curious and enthusiast soul, and a firm believer that Everything happens at right time and for good.</p>
            
            <p>This blog is my digital corner of the world where I pour out thoughts, stories, code, food cravings, travel diaries, and everything in between. Whether I'm debugging My Code, discovering a hidden food joint, or chasing sunsets in a new city — I love capturing experiences and turning them into words.</p>
            
            <p>I started this blog to document the chaos, calm, and creativity that life throws at me — and to connect with people like you who find joy in the little things, learning in mistakes, and magic in the everyday.</p>
            
            <p>When I'm not blogging, you'll probably find me:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Writing code and breaking it (and fixing it :-))</li>
                <li>Sipping chai while doodling ideas</li>
                <li>Planning trips I may or may not take</li>
                <li>Trying to recreate a dish I saw on YouTube</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Thanks for stopping by — feel free to explore, share, and say hi!</p>
            </section>
        </div>

        <h2 id="recent-posts">Recent Posts -</h2>
        <div class="posts-container">
            <% posts.forEach(post => { %>
                <article class="post-card">
                    <h3><%= post.title %></h3>
                    <p class="post-excerpt"><%= post.content.substring(0, 100) %>...</p>
                    <div class="post-meta">
                        <span class="post-date"><%= post.createdAt.toDateString() %></span>
                        <a href="/posts/<%= post._id %>" class="read-more">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </article>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
    </main>

    <section id="leave-note" class="leave-note-section">
        <h2>Have something to say - leave a note</h2>
        <form action="/notes" method="POST" class="leave-note-form">
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

            <label for="contact">Contact No. or Email:</label>
            <input type="text" id="contact" name="contact" required>

            <label for="message">Message:</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
